CloudRaker
 is looking for a 
Senior

Full-stack Developer
 to help us create innovative products and best-in-class digital experiences for our clients. Our ideal candidate is eager to learn about, and experiment with, existing &amp; emerging web technologies, and loves identifying ways to automate processes. The candidate would primarily develop pharmaceutical and retail industry websites




tl;dr We’re looking for a Senior Full-stack Developer with JavaScript/TypeScript and React knowledge. Spread: 45% Front, 45% Back-end, 10% DevOps. Daily work will include Product Development and/or Digital Agency Projects. Full time, based in Canada as long as you can work in the Montreal time zone (we’re working for home at the moment).





Your day-to-day: 







Develop, implement and maintain web projects with HTML, (S)CSS, JS;



Perform code walkthroughs and code reviews;


Create unit tests for your own code; 

Work collaboratively with various teams to conceive, build and launch jaw-dropping websites, applications, as well as integrate CMS;

Able to work independently in an environment of continuous integration and deployment;

Take part in planning &amp; developing great products using cutting-edge technologies;

Challenging yourself and the team to find more efficient ways to work and new technologies to experiment with. 






You have: 



5+ years experience of working in a Full-stack developer role;

An educational background in Computer Science/Engineering or equivalent hands-on experience;

Strong knowledge of, and experience with, core Web technology:

HTML5

CSS/SCSS

JavaScript/ES6

Node JS / React based technologies

Git

Responsive Web design

SEO

Familiarity with (the more the better)

PHP Frameworks/CMS (esp. WordPress and Laravel)

Grid-based frameworks such as Bootstrap or Foundation

TypeScript

The ability to juggle multiple projects and prioritize tasks;

Experience with Linux and basic shell scripting; 

Experience working with e-commerce platforms (nice-to-have);

Experience working with email-based marketing platform (nice-to-have);

Agency experience (nice-to-have);

Pharma and Retail knowledge or experience (nice-to-have)

Experience with WCAG AA standard (nice-to-have);

Experience with Strapi or Apostrophe CMS (nice-to-have);

Experience with Nest.JS(nice-to-have);

Experience working with API First and Headless CMS paradigms (nice-to-have);

Application development using React Native or other technologies (nice-to-have);






You are: 



A “clean coder”;

A team player, who loves sharing ideas and knowledge with others;

Always looking for ways to keep your code clean, tight and maintainable;

Someone who can deliver high quality code while adhering to web development best practices;

Passionate about staying informed about new technology, trends and best practices;

An entrepreneur at heart, with a ‘get it done’ attitude;

An easy going, light-hearted person who doesn’t take themselves too seriously;

Able to stay cool as a cucumber... even when deadlines are looming;

English speaking, or even better, bilingual (French);






About CloudRaker:


With offices in Montreal and Toronto, CloudRaker specializes in delivering leading-edge marketing and technology solutions that connect consumers &amp; commerce through meaningful brand experiences. We’re not your average agency. We work hard but don’t take ourselves too seriously. We’re a tight knit team of gif-loving, franglais-speaking, meme-makers, who collaborate to do great things. We don’t just make people want things, we make things people want.




___





Développeur Full-Stack






CloudRaker
 est à la recherche d’un(e) 
Développeur(se) Full-Stack
 pour aider nos clients à réaliser des expériences numériques à couper le souffle, mais également à aider CloudRaker à développer des produits innovants pour la nouvelle ère du commerce du détail. Notre candidat idéal est avide d’apprendre et d’expérimenter avec des technologies du web existantes &amp; émergentes, et adore identifier des façons d’automatiser des processus. Le candidat travaillera principalement au développement de sites pharmaceutiques ou dans le commerce du détail.. 




